'''International Project for a Participatory Society'''

URL = http://www.zmag.org/ipps.html


=Description=

"The International Project for a Participatory Society (IPPS) is a group of activists, writers, media producers, and others committed to the basic principles and values of solidarity, diversity, equity, self management. Our mandate is to generate, promote, and support vision and strategy for attaining a participatory society. This site details our definition and operations and presents links for content regarding social change vision and strategy that we have generated or that we feel special regard for."

